@HealthChecksDemo_HostAddress = http://localhost:5072

### Get service information (root endpoint)
GET {{HealthChecksDemo_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### Health check - Liveness probe
GET {{HealthChecksDemo_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###

### Health check - Readiness probe
GET {{HealthChecksDemo_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

